                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4906" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0271</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8644 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自觉觉他：京博仁孝文化进阶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chambroad Group’s Benevolence and Filial Piety Culture Evolution： Eelf-inspire and Inspire Others</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王德胜，辛杰，韩杰，李婷婷，屠云峰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">培训部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">33 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京博集团；仁孝文化；自觉觉他；进阶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chambroad holding group; benevolence and filial piety culture; self-inspire and inspire others; evolution</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京博这家曾经困囿于连年亏损的润滑油脂厂在马韵升的带领下，用了二十余年的时间成长为拥有四大板块、九大产业、面向国际的现代化集团，稳居中国企业五百强。京博发展的历程印证：企业家的文化自觉在企业发展过程中不断的觉他，影响一大批京博同仁及利益相关者集体向善，京博以“仁孝”为底色的企业文化与企业发展高度融合。本案例以京博集团发展历程和“仁孝”文化演变为主线，通过描述京博在不同发展阶段的“仁孝”文化特征及具体实践，重点探讨什么是京博“仁孝”文化、如何构建以“仁孝”为核心的京博文化管理体系、企业家如何基于“仁孝”自觉觉他，以及如何将国学文化智慧与现代企业管理实践有机融合等问题。本案例可以为企业通过国学文化重塑企业文化管理、实现企业持续健康发展提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chambroad, a lubricating grease plant that had been trapped in successive years of losses, led by Ma Yunsheng, spent more than 20 years to grow into a modern group with four major sectors, nine major industries, and an international orientation, which is firmly established as a Chinese company Top 500. The development history of Chambroad shows that the entrepreneur’s cultural consciousness constantly affects a large number of Chambroad colleagues and stakeholders to collectively be good in the process of enterprise development. Chambroad’s culture based on benevolent and filial piety is highly integrated with corporate development. This case study is based on the development history of Chambroad Group and the evolution of benevolence and filial piety culture. By describing the cultural characteristics and specific practices of benevolence and filial piety culture in different development stages, this case study focuses on what is the benevolence and filial piety culture and how to construct Chambroad culture management system with benevolence and filial piety as the core, how entrepreneurs consciously inspire themselves, and how to integrate the traditional Chinese cultural wisdom with modern enterprise management practices. This case can provide a reference for enterprises to reshape corporate culture management through Sinology culture and achieve sustainable and healthy development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业文化》、《商业伦理与企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化、人力资源管理、企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-11</td>
